            <title>[CASSANDRA-7580] Super user cannot list permissions with cqlsh</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-7580</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On a system configured with:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;PasswordAuthenticator&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;CassandraAuthorizer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;If you login as a super user and issue:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;list all permissions;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;where permissions have been granted to a user you get back:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Keyspace None not found.
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
